https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1u5mA9J5FTg&spfreload=10   create and publish cordova

install node, android sdk, ant, cordova (npm install -g cordova)
create progect: cordova create CordovaProject io.cordova.hellocordova CordovaApp
add android: cordova platform add android
build: cordova build android
run: cordova emulate android   or cordova run android   or install phonegap and run: phonegap serve


Key generation syntax
keytool -genkey -v -keystore app-key.keystore -alias app-key -keyalg RSA -keysize 2048 -validity 10000
create build.pom to root directory
run: cordova build android --release    it grab key file. new apk file apploud
